Package: HealthViz
Title: Statistical Analysis and Visualization Tools for Data Science
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Gabriel","Lopez", email = "glopezmayer@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: HealthViz provides tools for analyzing and visualizing health data, 
    supporting epidemiology and public health analysis. It includes functions 
    for plotting epidemic curves, conducting survival analysis, and calculating 
    risk ratios, tailored to the needs of health data analysts and researchers.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, survival, survminer
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2

